          <div data-review id="electrolux-well-q8">
            <span data-tag>Eficienta Maxima</span>
            <h2>Electrolux Well Q8</h2>
            <div data-specs>
              <span><strong>Putere aspiratie:</strong> Pana la 128 AW</span>
              <span><strong>Autonomie baterie:</strong> Pana la 50 minute</span>
